Nonsensical trash. 

A show about the one being in the universe who would never 'help' humanity 'helping' humanity. I don't know if there is a devil - but if there is he is the inhuman, murky, sinister, malicious incarnation of utter evil - heartless, void of pity, delighting at every infant's death and every cancer patient's cough. And here we see a charming, handsome 'hero' who...

Oh, why bother? The world's utter stupidity is just not worth getting into rages over.

I've had my little say. 

In my opinion it's like making a movie with Stalin, Mao or Hitler as the hero.